<html>
<head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.5.0/pure-min.css">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css">

</head>


<body>
	<div class="pure-g">
		<div class="pure-u-1">
			<h1>Essay Extender</h1>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="pure-g">
		<div class="pure-u-1-2">
		
			<form method="post" action="/">
				<textarea name="input" rows:"60" cols="70">Your essay goes here</textarea>
				<input type="submit" name="button" value="Submit">
			</form>

			<h2>Welcome!</h2>
			<p>Have you ever written an awesome essay but then realized it was too short? FRUSTRATING! Well we have a solution! The days you have to double-space your essay or increase the margins are over. To make your essay longer, protracted, drawn-out, far-reaching, outstretched, spread out and spun out, just paste it into the textfield below and click the "Submit" button.</p>

		</div>
		<div class="pure-u-1-2">
		<h2>Result:</h2>
		 	<%= @translation %>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>